{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"36201-fishing-in-my-village","title":"Fishing in My Village","description":"This picture book describes various fishing techniques – from fishing with traditional rods to using nets. The entire village in this story has gone for fishing. Let’s go fish with them!","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sanjana  Khoobchandani"],"illustrators":["Nivong  Sengsakoun"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/36201-fishing-in-my-village"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93896/size3/94d5619b2dd7478c430b5dc5f669a763.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93896/size6/94d5619b2dd7478c430b5dc5f669a763.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69016/size6/cec052c592cd8a2ac8dd7b33402383e5.jpg","text":"Last night, it\nrained so hard that water overflowed the river banks. \nThe villagers got excited and started fishing!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69017/size6/6523b7a09f6059bc53ad23f1c9d55520.jpg","text":"Thao Thong fished\nwith a hook and line, and caught a big striped snakehead fish.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69018/size6/9b7795c9be415864fc6a5c096bc69f4c.jpg","text":"Nang Khambai fished\nwith a fishing cage and caught a silver barb.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69019/size6/2764addbdb98e02adffbf5bc8101aad0.jpg","text":"Nang Bouakhao’s fishing\nnet caught shrimp.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69020/size6/f08ca12279dcaf7de96838370bb330fe.jpg","text":"Grandfather Boun\nused a cast net to catch an Asian red-tailed catfish.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69021/size6/d11ac55e55a85ca9a86b2e8539a97885.jpg","text":"Thao Kood fished\nwith gillnets and caught mud crabs.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69022/size6/9d90a12722f0621454e54167691f2995.jpg","text":"Grandmother Pheng\nfished with lift nets and caught river carp.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69023/size6/9e5b378002ebb4b3907d10cad917cb08.jpg","text":"Uncle Khampiew used\na trap and caught catfish.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69024/size6/fd6f8badd1bd5c0d7cc4e2e4bf5a6d8e.jpg","text":"Aunt Khamsouk went spin fishing and caught a broadhead walking catfish.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69025/size6/75b9b40c9d1c8f082dcc9d0cf2f647df.jpg","text":"Thao So fished with\na pole and line and caught a basa fish.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69026/size6/7c2977d4d40707846a0775d87ae815f1.jpg","text":"At noon, the\nvillagers enjoyed their catch.  \nThey cooked all the fish and had lunch together by the river.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69027/size6/ebb1c23adb8da2b8f81e0f4e17864dd5.jpg","text":"13/13","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":135}}